<h2>Swollen lips and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms swollen lips and white patches on tongue including Thrush (infants and children), Thrush (adults), and Kawasaki disease.</p>
